  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planetary Conflict: 2301 is a multiplayer third person shooter game set in the future, with two factions pit against each other: The Lunar Federation and the Planetary Union.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-4 Multiplayer maps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Co-op Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-5 Gamemodes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-9 character models</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Character loadouts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-1 Vehicle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-First person toggle using P key</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 Different Weapons: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Sniper RIfle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-2 Assault Rifles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-3 Pistols </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Shotgun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Flashbang</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Frag Grenade</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Smoke Grenade</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planetary Conflict: 2301 is a multiplayer third person shooter game set in the future, with two factions pit against each other: The Lunar Federation and the Planetary Union.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-4 Multiplayer maps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Co-op Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-5 Gamemodes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-9 character models</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Character loadouts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-1 Vehicle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-First person toggle using P key</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 Different Weapons: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Sniper RIfle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-2 Assault Rifles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-3 Pistols </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Shotgun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Flashbang</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Frag Grenade</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Smoke Grenade</p>",
